vistra.framework.traversal

Interface ITraversal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBidirectIterator<IStep>, java.util.Iterator<IStep>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Traversal

    public interface ITraversal
extends IBidirectIterator<IStep>
    An interface for a traversal as an immutable, bidirectional iterator over steps. A step contains one or more commands each of them modifying the graph.
    Author:
    Roland Bruggmann (brugr9@bfh.ch)
